 19/7/18 Edinburgh Spent the morn indoor and then went down with the Colonel to Royal Bank of Scotland and saw the mgr . ? a creep crawl look man . Walk to the N. B. Hotel and there lunch and had a quiet talk befor return to Abercrombi Place where the Col . took me to see a Dr. and got a prescript for a tonic . Took Sheila out for a walk and had a good stroll round all the shop portion of the town after which we return for dinner . It was anoth long day and still daylight at 10.30 when we went to bed . Yarn over whiski and soda until a late hour on ani amount varieti of subject . Audrey at Carron has influenza Sheila had to go to bed with the same .
